text: Spiral: From The Book of Saw, or simply Spiral, is a 2021 American horror movie. The movie is the ninth installment in the Saw franchise. It was directed by Darren Lynn Bousman, and written by Josh Stolberg and Peter Goldfinger. The movie stars Chris Rock, Samuel L. Jackson, Max Minghella, and Marisol Nichols. ==References== Category:2021 horror movies Category:American horror movies Category:Saw movies Category:Lionsgate movies Category:Movies directed by Darren Lynn Bousman
